  <div class='modal-body' >
      <p>There are some nice keyboard shortcuts for more productive mind-mapping:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create a new child node by pressing <strong>Tab</strong></li>
        <li>Create a new sibling  node by pressing <strong>Enter</strong></li>
        <li>Edit the current node by pressing <strong>Space</strong></li>
        <li>Delete the node by pressing <strong>Backspace</strong> or <strong>Delete</strong></li>
        <li>Use arrow keys to navigate around the map</li>
        <li>When editing, just press <strong>Enter</strong> to complete editing, or cancel the editing by pressing <strong>Escape</strong></li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can also navigate using your mouse:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Click a node to select it</li>
        <li>Double-click to edit</li>
        <li>Drag &amp; drop nodes to reorder or change parents</li>
        <li>Click and drag outside nodes to move the entire map</li>
      </ul>
